title: Bipartisan Relief, SEC, Market Regulation
itunes:title: Bipartisan Relief, SEC, Market Regulation
description:
Host: Jeanne Sheehan Zaino. Guests: Rick Davis, Bloomberg contributor, Partner at Stone Court Capital, former campaign manager for John McCain's 2008 presidential campaign, former Alaska Senator Mark Begich, Strategic Consulting Advisor at Brownstein Hyatt Farber Schreck, and Norm Champ, Partner at Kirkland & Ellis and former Director of the Division of Investment Management at the SEC.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
